*cucumber-0.3.104 (28 Sep 2009)

  28 Sep 2009; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +cucumber-0.3.104.ebuild:
  Version bump with support for steps in more programming languages.

*cucumber-0.3.103 (24 Sep 2009)

  24 Sep 2009; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +cucumber-0.3.103.ebuild:
  Version bump.

*cucumber-0.3.101 (19 Sep 2009)

  19 Sep 2009; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +cucumber-0.3.101.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  * New pdf formatter
  * Step Argument Transforms
  * Adding webrat steps for asserting content does or does not exist within 
    a particular element

  19 Sep 2009; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -cucumber-0.3.96.ebuild,
